        :code(lang='html')
          /replacement_folder
              |── /project_folder
              |── classes.txt
              |── replace.bat
        p.-text
          | 3. Open <code>replace.bat</code> with IDE and change variable <code>PROJECT_SRC</code> with the path corresponding to your project folder:
        :code(lang='html')
          set "PROJECT_SRC=project_folder"
        p.-text
          | 5. Launch <code>replace.bat</code> script ( doubleclick on the file )
        p.-text
          | 6. Make sure that Atomic prefixes are correctly replaced
